NAME
	this_player - get the current 'player'

SYNOPSIS
	object this_player()

DESCRIPTION
	Get the object representing the current 'player', i.e.  the living 
	object which has 'given the last command'. 

RETURN VALUE
	The object representing the current player is returned.

SEE ALSO
	players, set_this_player, this_body, this_connection, 
	this_environment, this_program, this_race, this_user

